==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: dosimeter badge
<hw>do*sim"et*er badge</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a dosimeter
consisting of a radiation-sensitive material, such as film, worn in a
small package on a person's clothing, to record the accumulated
radiation exposure of the person over a period of time; -- used to
monitor the exposure of individuals, such as workers in a nuclear power
plant, to ionizing radiation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>dosimetry</ent>⟦br⟧
